    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >【注意】请确保您的电脑满足下面所述的配置要求：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1、您需要任意一套支持SteamVR的头显。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2、请确保您使用的是NVIDIA 3060及以上的显卡，AMD Intel显卡现在暂不支持。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3、请确保JUMPWORK相机接口连接了2个单独不共享带宽的USB3.0接口。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-你想在VR里拥有自己的腿？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-还在折腾半小时，游玩十分钟？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-受够了穿戴式全追的麻烦？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-试过了其他无穿戴全身追踪，完全不能用？延迟太高，飘来飘去？只支持单摄，转身就会丢失追踪？ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >————————————————————————————————————————</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >试试由JUMPWORK.AI带来的极简的技术方案： </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >由1台或2台深度相机带来360度无穿戴高精度的全身追踪</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-1秒设置完毕 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-提供多达9个Tracker覆盖了您的下半身和您的手肘部 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302940/extras/c3aac0cc3f98d37b6f4b1ac0c90161d3.poster.avif?t=1731665040\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302940/extras/c3aac0cc3f98d37b6f4b1ac0c90161d3.webm?t=1731665040\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302940/extras/c3aac0cc3f98d37b6f4b1ac0c90161d3.mp4?t=1731665040\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >————————————————————————————————————————</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-它能用来干什么？可以用来炫耀、跳舞、当然最重要的，您可以随时踹您想踹的人 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302940/extras/ebc73761039e96cf4a84e26c5fec2b63.poster.avif?t=1731665040\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302940/extras/ebc73761039e96cf4a84e26c5fec2b63.webm?t=1731665040\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302940/extras/ebc73761039e96cf4a84e26c5fec2b63.mp4?t=1731665040\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >———————————————————————————————————————— </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-可以实现原地踏步移动*，让你在VR里也能拥有自己的腿</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302940/extras/1e6ee1a462ffab467fdd8a6d132799da.poster.avif?t=1731665040\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302940/extras/1e6ee1a462ffab467fdd8a6d132799da.webm?t=1731665040\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302940/extras/1e6ee1a462ffab467fdd8a6d132799da.mp4?t=1731665040\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >————————————————————————————————————————</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302940/extras/7ce9b4204fe1eef7c50bbef3314ce159.avif?t=1731665040\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302940/extras_big/7ce9b4204fe1eef7c50bbef3314ce159.avif?t=1731665040 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-可以实现三维重建，导入Unity中后用在VRChat里，也可以重建一些小物体*</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >————————————————————————————————————————</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302940/extras/233260d45875210ef9235ccdb55b0427.avif?t=1731665040\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302940/extras_big/233260d45875210ef9235ccdb55b0427.avif?t=1731665040 width=800 height=446 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-对于工作室用户，我们提供一种低成本的录制骨骼数据文件的方法（动作捕捉）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >————————————————————————————————————————</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >提示：*代表功能未仍在测试阶段，我们会再合适的时候上线测试版本，并随时可能会下线直到功能稳定。</p>",
